      • approveShiftChangeEmployee

        private static boolean approveShiftChangeEmployee(NewsFeedItem newsFeedItem,
                                                  boolean shiftAccepted)
        Employee accepts or rejects an offered shift (where they have set themselves as available). If rejected: method checks if there are other employees who have not accepted/rejected the new shift. If there are none pending, method sends notification to admin
        Parameters:
        newsFeedItem - - the ID of the news feed notification
        shiftAccepted - - boolean if shift is accepted or not
        Returns:
        True if succesfully made notification
